<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>验证码通知</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --main-color: #3f3f3f;
      --text-color: #444;
      --bg-color: #ffffff;
      --gray: #7f8c8d;
      --border-color: #e9ecef;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f1f3f5;
      color: var(--text-color);
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 520px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: var(--bg-color);
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      padding: 32px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    }

    .header {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--main-color);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .content {
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .code-box {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: var(--main-color);
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      text-align: center;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      user-select: all;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    }

    .button {
      color: #e9ecef;
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: var(--main-color);
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 14px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .button:hover {
      color: #3f3f3f;
      background-color: #e2e2e2;
    }

    .footer {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--gray);
      margin-top: 32px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">验证码通知</div>
    <div class="content">
      您正在进行身份验证，请在 <strong>5 分钟内</strong> 完成操作。
    </div>
    <div class="code-box" id="code"><%= code %></div>
    <a href="#" class="button" onclick="copyCode(event)">复制验证码</a>
    <div class="footer">
      若非本人操作，请忽略此邮件。<br/>
      © 2025 7Z All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    function copyCode(e) {
      e.preventDefault();
      const codeText = document.getElementById('code').innerText.trim();
      navigator.clipboard.writeText(codeText).then(() => {
        alert('验证码已复制到剪贴板');
      }).catch(err => {
        alert('复制失败，请手动复制');
      });
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>